# Cloudflare Pages Redirects Configuration

# Static assets — must come BEFORE the SPA catch-all or Cloudflare Pages
# serves index.html for every asset request (confirmed white-screen bug 2026-05-15)
/assets/*    /assets/:splat    200

# Direct file serve for LLM discovery
/llms.txt    /llms.txt    200
/llms.json   /llms.json   200

# SPA fallback for React Router (client-side routes only)
/*    /index.html   200
